學習規範 Course Policy
課程要求 Course Requirements:

(一)專題演講 Guest Lecturers
(a) 每次演講後撰寫演講心得，並於演講隔週繳交。
(a) Reports for each invited speech will be due the following week.
(b) 中文演講心得可用中文撰寫報告，但須包含英文摘要及關鍵字。
(b) A report can be written in Chinese in the case of a lecture given in Chinese, but it should include an English abstract and keywords.
(c) 請協助專題演講之服務工作，例如：演講者接送等。
(c) Assistance with the preparation of the talk (for example, welcoming the guest lecturer).
 
(二)讀書簡報  Presentation of Study
(1) 排定為書心得報告之週次，每週由2位同學報告，每位修課同學本學期須準備3次書簡報，每次簡報每位學生準備3篇著作。
(1) Preparing the student presentation schedule: Each student will present three times during the semester, with two students presenting each week (excluding dates of guest lecturers). Each student presentation will focus on three scholarly and/or pioneering publications.  
(2) 每位學生於3/12(四)下午5點前將3次讀書簡報的主題寄交助教，並於3/13課堂討論同學報告的排序。
(2) Each student will select three topics by the second week. Please send your list to the teaching assistant no later than 5:00 pm (1700) on March 12th, so that the lists can be compiled to create the presentation schedule. This schedule will be used for discussion during the class of March 13th.
(3)每次簡報內容至少包含3篇以上期刊文章，內容包括：(1)每篇文章的主旨；(2)比較三篇文章的內容，例如指出作者觀點的異同、文章內容是否互補或相反。請以英文進簡報，並製作powerpoint簡報檔，以至少15頁、至多30頁為準。
(3) Each student's presentation will consist of three scholarly and/or pioneering publications in which the presenter first explains the essential ideas of each (separately), and then compares them. The comparison should identify the essential similarities and differences of the authors' ideas, and/or identify where the ideas complement or oppose each other. Presentations will be given in English with PowerPoint (PPT), using at least 15 slides and no more than 30.
(4)簡報者對每篇文章須提出摘要、關鍵字、重要引句。
(4) For each publication, the presenter should provide an abstract, keywords, and quotations in the presentation.
(5)簡報順序請各位同學於第三週(3/13)上課時排定，並將排定名單繳交給助教，若需更動簡報順序或文章，請至少於一週前通知全班師生。
(5) The order of presentation will be arranged during the third week of the course. Please submit your reading list to the teaching assistant. If you need to change your presentation week or readings, please inform the class at least a week ahead of time.  
(6)每次簡報請於一周前將簡報之三篇文章以PDF 方式上傳至moodle，簡報檔最慢於簡報前一天上傳至moodle，簡報者須於課堂上準備簡報檔紙本給四位授課老師。
(6) Upload the selected articles to Moodle in PDF format a week before the presentation. Submit the PPT to Moodle at least 24 hours before the presentation. Prepare printouts (hardcopies) of the PPT (two slides per page, double-sided) for each instructor on the presentation day.



       

